Content.bodyText:
Hi Darren!

Having been a fan of your blog for a while, I was wondering if you could (if you haven't already) make an index listing all the pho cafes you've been to, either in order by area or ratings. Then I could print them out for easy reference and follow in your footsteps :-)

Thanks!
